dynamic` being present in both parent and child layers. JPMS allows for this, but if the source module descriptor matches fully with the target, it might trigger a `LayerInstantiationException`. The subprocess also only probes test classes, which is good, but I’m a bit unsure about invoking package-private main methods in non-public classes — can Java do that?\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring visibility and compile issues**\\n\\nI’m wondering if the class not being public affects whether the launcher can still access its public main method. Even if the class itself isn’t public, it seems like it could still work. I've seen instances like `ModuleReadEdgeProbe`, which is package-private but still functioning. A potential compile error comes to mind since there’s a public class alongside a package-private one in the same file. Then there's the question of whether `copyLibraryClasses` to the target module root handles all classes properly. The `module-info.java` being compiled correctly is essential too.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Updated `NexusAccessorInnerDispatcherInnerCreationActionTest.java` to target the remaining fallback-path call sites for:\n\n`reactor.blockhound.shaded.net.bytebuddy.dynamic.NexusAccessor$Dispatcher$CreationAction`\n\nChanges made:\n- Added `childFirstAccessorWithoutResourcesFallsBackToSystemNexus()`:\n  - Loads a child-first copy of `NexusAccessor`/`Nexus` with `ByteArrayClassLoader.PersistenceHandler.LATENT`.\n  - This hides class resources from the copied accessor, forcing the fallback path that calls `ClassLoader#loadClass` and fallback `Class#getMethod` calls.\n- Reworked the named-module test to launch a bounded subprocess:\n  - Loads system `Nexus` from a named target module.\n  - Defines a source module from an in-memory `ModuleFinder` whose `ModuleReader` can load classes but hides class resources.\n  - This is designed to force fallback and exercise the reflective `Module#addReads` `Method#invoke` path.\n\nI did not run the Gradle test command.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07066c0709a9ed1a0169faad590d588190a7f603ebbd01f592\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 992, "output": 1043, "cacheRead": 57856, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 59891, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778036044496, "responseId": "resp_07066c0709a9ed1a0169faad4d20c48190aa87433cbccf5121"}, "toolResults": []}
